India’s Aditya Birla Group May Bid for Whitehaven, Standard Says

-- B y   R a k t e e m   K a t a k e y
-- 
2011-03-14T01:02:42Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-14/india-s-aditya-birla-group-may-bid-for-whitehaven-standard-says.html
  India ’s Aditya Birla group has been
selected to bid for  Whitehaven Coal Ltd. (WHC)  and may make a formal
offer for the Australian company, the Business Standard
newspaper reported, citing three unidentified people.  About 20 companies may be interested in Whitehaven,
according to the report.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
